# mac-bootstrap

Read [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) for full context. Use skills in `.cursor/skills/` for workflows.

## Constraints

- Bash 3.2+ only. No bash 4+ syntax.
- Install targets in `config/*.yaml` — never hardcode in scripts.
- `Brewfile` is generated — `make brewfile` after `apps.yaml` / `cli.yaml` edits.
- `bootstrap.sh` sources scripts — logic inside functions only.
- YAML via Ruby helpers in `scripts/helpers.sh` — no `yq`.
- Helpers: `log_*`, `run_cmd`, `run_sudo`, `yaml_*`, `run_bootstrap_step`, `die`.

## Before finishing

1. `make test` — update `tests/run_tests.sh` counts if config lists changed
2. `make lint`
3. Prefer `./bootstrap.sh --add-app/cli/mas` for new items

## Safety

- `--dry-run` / `make dry-run` for bootstrap changes
- No credentials in repo
- `validation.strict` in profiles is not implemented
